# R32Garage

Luxury automotive landing page built with Vite, React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

## Development

```sh
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Build

```sh
npm run build
```

## Deployment (GitHub Pages)
- Pages URL: `https://<your-github-username>.github.io/R32Garage/`
- Vite `base` is set to `/R32Garage/` for project pages.
- In GitHub repo settings: **Pages → Source = GitHub Actions**.
- Workflow: `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` builds on pushes to `main`/`master`, uploads `dist`, and deploys via `actions/deploy-pages`.

## Notes
- Tailwind is configured via `tailwind.config.js` and `postcss.config.js`.
- If you fork/rename, update `vite.config.ts` `base` to match the new repo name and adjust the Pages URL above.
